subject: Home page
description: As a user i want to create a home page so that i can navigate to required pages

subject: Add players
description: As a user i want add players so that people can participate in the planning poker exercise

subject: View current players
description: AS a developer i want to create a page so that i can view current players list

subject: Remove players
description: As a user i want to remove players from the game so that I can remove existing players and add new players for the exercise

subject: Start game
description:
As a dealer  
I want to start the game at the click of a button  
So that, the poker planning can be done by all the players

subject: Current Votes
description:
As a dealer  
I want to view the current votes   
So that I can see the status of voting  in progress

subject: Reset votes
description: As a developer i want to create a log so that i can reset the votes on an issue

subject: View current Issue
description: As a user, I want to view the current issue so that I can vote for that issue.

subject: check User count
description: As a developer, I want to check the number of users so that I can see how many users are currently participating.

subject: show report
description: As a developer, I want to create a button to see the report so that I can have a summary of how many votes were given to certain issues and by whom.

subject: Exit
description:
As a player  
I want to have a button for Exit

So that I can quit the GUI client and the game easily.

subject: Help
description: As a user, I want to create a help page so that the player can know about the game

subject: Type of Poker (Modern Poker/Texas Hold 'em)
description: Texas Hold'em is probably the most played game and it is the first version of Poker. Now we also find Modern Poker interesting.

subject: The Showdown
description: The Highest Five-card hand wins the pot!

subject: Shuffle and Cut
description: The dealer shuffles the deck and then distributes cards to seated players.

subject: Pre-Flop
description: Here a player can fold, call, raise or even re-raise depending on your cards.

subject: Add Issues from GUI client
description:
As a player
I want provision to add issues from the GUI client
So that I can choose an issue file and add before starting the game.
